toaststunt-pl — License
========================

This project has a layered history, and its license follows that history:

    LambdaMOO (Xerox PARC, Pavel Curtis et al., 1990-1996)
      -> Stunt (Todd Sundsted et al.)
        -> ToastStunt (lisdude and contributors, https://github.com/lisdude/toaststunt)
          -> toaststunt-pl (this fork, Radoslaw Smolka, 2026-),
             https://github.com/totalzero/toaststunt-pl

Neither LambdaMOO, Stunt, nor ToastStunt ever published a single top-level
LICENSE file. Instead, permissive license notices are embedded directly in
the header of most individual source files. This file collects and
documents those notices so the terms are easy to find in one place, and
states the terms for new work added in this fork. It does not replace or
override the original per-file notices — where a source file carries one of
the notices below in its header, that notice still applies to that file.

If you modify a file that carries one of these notices, keep the existing
header intact and add your own copyright line underneath it, rather than
replacing it.


