4. Bundled third-party dependencies
--------------------------------------

These are vendored libraries with their own, separate licenses. They are
unmodified by this project and keep their original terms in full:

- `src/dependencies/LICENSE_THPOOL` — MIT License, Copyright (c) 2016 Johan
  Hanssen Seferidis.
- `src/dependencies/yajl/COPYING` — BSD-style license, Copyright 2010,
  Lloyd Hilaiel.

See those files directly for the authoritative text.


