Summary for downstream users
--------------------------------

- You may use, copy, modify and redistribute this software, including for
  commercial purposes.
- Preserve existing copyright notices in files that carry them (sections
  1-3 above); add your own notice alongside them when you modify such a
  file.
- New code contributed in this fork (section 5) is available under the MIT
  License.
- No copyleft obligation applies anywhere in this codebase: you are not
  required to publish your own modifications, though the community around
  LambdaMOO/Stunt/ToastStunt has traditionally kept its code open.


